hadiths[18]{hadithnumber,text}:
2239,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to (Madina ke) log phalon mein aik saal ya 2 saal ke liye sauda-Salam kartey they. ya unhon-ne ye kaha ke 2 saal aur teen saal (ke liye kartey they) shak Ismail ko hua tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs bhi khajoor mein sauda-Salam karey, usey muqarrara paimaaney ya muqarrara wazan ke sath karni chahiye"
2240,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to log khajoor mein 2 aur teen saal tak ke liye Sauda Salam kartey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hidayat farmai ke jisey kisi cheez ka sauda-Salam karna hai, usey muqarrara wazan aur muqarrara muddat ke liye thehra kar kare."
2241,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madeena) tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke muqarrara wazan aur muqarrara muddat tak ke liye (sauda Salam) honii chahiye
2242,"Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad-bin-al-Haad aur abu-Barda mein Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq aapasii ikhtilaf hua. to un hazraat ne mujhey ibne-abii-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. chunanche maine unse puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke ham Rasulullah (sl), Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamanon mein geihun, jau, Munaqqaa aur khajoor ke saudey-Salam kartey they. phir maine ibne-Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne bhi yahi jawab diya."
2243,"Abdullaah-bin-Ahaddaad-bin-al-Haad aur abu-Barda mein Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq aapasii ikhtilaf hua. to un hazraat ne mujhey ibne-abii-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. chunanche maine unse puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke ham Rasulullah (sl), Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamanon mein geihun, jau, munaqqaa aur khajoor ke saudey Salam kartey they. phir maine ibn-Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne bhi yahi jawab diya."
2244,"mujhey Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad aur abu-Barda ne Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bheja aur hidayat ki ke unse poochho ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab aap ke zamaney mein gehun ka sauda-Salam kartey they? Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke ham Sham (Syria) ke Anbaat (eik kaashtkaar qaum (ke sath geihun, Juwaar, Zaitoon ki muqarrara wazan aur muqarrara muddat ke liye saudaa kya kartey they. maine puchha kya sirf usi shakhs se aap log ye Sauda kya kartey they jiske paas asl maal maujood hota tha? unhon-ne farmaya ke ham uske mutaalliq poochhtey hi nahi they. iske baad un donon hazraat ne mujhey Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza (Raziallahu anhu) ke khidmat mein bhejaa. maine unse bhi poochha. unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab aap ke ahade-mubaarak mein Sauda Salam kya kartey they aur ham ye bhi nahi poochhtey they ke unke kheti bhi hai ya nahi. ham se Is'haaq-bin-Shaaheen ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne bayan kya, unse Shebani ne, unse Muhammad-bin-abii-Mujaalid ne yahi hadis is riwayat mein ye bayan ki ke ham unse gehun aur jau mein Sauda Salam kya kartey they. aur Abdullaah-bin-Waleed ne bayan kya, unse Sufiyan ne, unse Shebani ne bayan kya, usmein unhon-ne Zaitoon ka bhi naam liya hai. ham se Quteba ne bayan kya, unse Jarir ne bayan kya, unse Shebani ne, aur is mein bayan kya ke geihun, jau aur munaqqaa mein (sauda-Salam kya kartey they)."
2245,"mujhey Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad aur abu-Barda ne Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bheja aur hidayat ki ke unse poochho ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab aap ke zamaney mein gehun ka sauda-Salam kartey they? Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke ham Sham (Syria) ke Anbaat (eik kaashtkaar qaum (ke sath geihun, Juwaar, Zaitoon ki muqarrara wazan aur muqarrara muddat ke liye saudaa kya kartey they. maine puchha kya sirf usi shakhs se aap log ye Sauda kya kartey they jiske paas asl maal maujood hota tha? unhon-ne farmaya ke ham uske mutaalliq poochhtey hi nahi they. iske baad un donon hazraat ne mujhey Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza (Raziallahu anhu) ke khidmat mein bhejaa. maine unse bhi poochha. unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab aap ke ahade-mubaarak mein Sauda Salam kya kartey they aur ham ye bhi nahi poochhtey they ke unke kheti bhi hai ya nahi. ham se Is'haaq-bin-Shaaheen ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne bayan kya, unse Shebani ne, unse Muhammad-bin-abii-Mujaalid ne yahi hadis is riwayat mein ye bayan ki ke ham unse gehun aur jau mein Sauda Salam kya kartey they. aur Abdullaah-bin-Waleed ne bayan kya, unse Sufiyan ne, unse Shebani ne bayan kya, usmein unhon-ne Zaitoon ka bhi naam liya hai. ham se Quteba ne bayan kya, unse Jarir ne bayan kya, unse Shebani ne, aur is mein bayan kya ke geihun, jau aur munaqqaa mein (sauda-Salam kya kartey they)."
2246,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor ke darakht mein Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne farmaya ke darakht par phal ko bechney se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt tak ke liye mana farmaya tha jab tak wo khaney ke qaabil na ho jaey ya uska wazan na kya ja sakey. aik shakhs ne puchha ke kya cheez wazan ki jaeygi. is par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb hi baithey huey aik shakhs ne kaha ke matlab ye hai ke andaza karne ke qaabil ho jaey aur Muaz ne bayan kya, unse Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Amr ne ke abul-Bakhtari ne kaha ke maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana kya tha. phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
2247,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor mein jabke wo darakht par lagi hui ho Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq poochha, to unhon-ne kaha ke jab tak wo kisi qaabil na ho jaey iske saude se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai. isi tarah chandi ko udhaar, naqd ke badley bechney se mana farmaya, phir maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor ke darakht par Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne bhi yahi kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt tak khajoor ke saudey se mana farmaya tha jab tak wo khaaii na ja sakey ya (ye farmaya ke) jab tak wo is qaabil na ho jaey ke usey koi kha sakey aur jab tak wo taulney ke qaabil na ho jaey."
2248,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor mein jabke wo darakht par lagi hui ho Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq poochha, to unhon-ne kaha ke jab tak wo kisi qaabil na ho jaey iske saude se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai. isi tarah chandi ko udhaar, naqd ke badley bechney se mana farmaya, phir maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor ke darakht par Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne bhi yahi kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt tak khajoor ke saudey se mana farmaya tha jab tak wo khaaii na ja sakey ya (ye farmaya ke) jab tak wo is qaabil na ho jaey ke usey koi kha sakey aur jab tak wo taulney ke qaabil na ho jaaey."
2249,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor ke darakht par Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phal ko us waqt tak bechney se mana farmaya hai jab tak wo nafa uthaney ke qaabil na ho jaey, isi tarah chandi ko soney ke badley bechney se jabke aik udhaar aur doosra naqd ho mana farmaya hai. phir maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ko darakht par bechney se jab tak wo khaney ke qaabil na ho jaey, isi tarah jab tak wo wazan karne ke qaabil na ho jaey mana farmaya hai. maine puchha ke wazan kiye janey ka kya matlab hai? to aik sahib ne jo unke paas baithey huey they kaha ke matlab ye hai ke jab tak wo is qaabil na ho jaey ke wo andaza ki ja sakey."
2250,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor ke darakht par Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phal ko us waqt tak bechney se mana farmaya hai jab tak wo nafa uthaney ke qaabil na ho jaey, isi tarah chandi ko soney ke badley bechney se jabke aik udhaar aur doosra naqd ho mana farmaya hai. phir maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ko darakht par bechney se jab tak wo khaney ke qaabil na ho jaey, isi tarah jab tak wo wazan karne ke qaabil na ho jaey mana farmaya hai. maine puchha ke wazan kiye janey ka kya matlab hai? to aik sahib ne jo unke paas baithey huey they kaha ke matlab ye hai ke jab tak wo is qaabil na ho jaey ke wo andaza ki ja sakey."
2251,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se udhaar ghalla khareedaa aur apni aik lohey ki zirah uske paas girwii rakhii.
2252,"ham ne Ibrahim Nakhai ke samney Sauda Salam mein girwii rakhney ka zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha ham se Aswad ne bayan kya, aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se aik muqarrara muddat ke liye ghalla khareedaa aur uske paas apni lohey ki zirah girwii rakh di thi."
2253,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to log phalon mein 2 aur teen saal tak ke liye Sauda Salam kya kartey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hidayat ki ke phalon mein Sauda Salam muqarrara paimaaney aur muqarrara muddat ke liye kya karo aur Abdullah-bin Waleed ne kaha ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha, unse-ibn-abii-Najeeh ne bayan kya, is riwayat mein yun hai ke ''paimaaney aur wazan ki ta'yun ke saath'' (sauda Salam honii chaahiye) ."
2254,"mujhey abu-Barda aur Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad ne Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza aur Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. maine un donon hazraat se Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ghaneemat ka maal paatey, phir Sham (Syria) ke Anbaat (eik kisaan qaum) hamarey yahan aatey to ham unse geihun, jau aur munaqqaa ke saudey Salam aik muddat muqarrar karke kar liya kartey they. unhon-ne kaha ke phir maine puchha ke unke paas us waqt ye cheezein maujood bhi hoti thin ya nahi? is par unhon-ne kaha ke ham iske mutaalliq unse kuchh poochhtey hi nahi they."
2255,"mujhey abu-Barda aur Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad ne Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza aur Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. maine un donon hazraat se Sauda Salam ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ghaneemat ka maal paatey, phir Sham (Syria) ke Anbaat (eik kisaan qaum) hamarey yahan aatey to ham unse geihun, jau aur munaqqaa ke saudey Salam aik muddat muqarrar karke kar liya kartey they. unhon-ne kaha ke phir maine puchha ke unke paas us waqt ye cheezein maujood bhi hoti thin ya nahi? is par unhon-ne kaha ke ham iske mutaalliq unse kuchh poochhtey hi nahi they."
2256,"log oont wghaira hamal ke hamal honey ki muddat tak ke liye bechtey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya, Naafe ne ( Hablil-Habla ( ki tafseer ye ki '' yahan tak ke ontni ke pet mein jo kuchh hai wo usey jaan ley.''"
